downstream signaling necessary for cytokine production and IFNG responses. This dampens the immune response, allowing cancer cells to survive despite PARPi treatment. Additionally, miR-181a can be transferred through extracellular vesicles, spreading resistance within the tumor microenvironment by suppressing STING in neighboring cells (
